about.summary: Support functions,  data sets, and vignettes for the 'psych' package. Contains several of the biggest data sets for the 'psych' package as well as one vignette. A few helper functions for file manipulation are included as well. For more information, see the <https://personality-project.org/r/> web page.

Support functions,  data sets, and vignettes for the 'psych' package. Contains several of the biggest data sets for the 'psych' package as well as one vignette. A few helper functions for file manipulation are included as well. For more information, see the <https://personality-project.org/r/> web page.

name: r-psychtools
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '2.1.6' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-psychtools
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/psychTools_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/psychTools/psychTools_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: a141a9e788c23df6963000c0b6a9c39ac925e2d49e3c0f0638d898e0aeab4de0

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic

  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
    - cross-r-base {{ r_base }}    # [build_platform != target_platform]

  host:
    - r-base
    - r-foreign
    - r-psych

  run:
    - r-base
    - r-foreign
    - r-psych

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('psychTools')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('psychTools')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://personality-project.org/r/psych/ https://personality-project.org/r/psych-manual.pdf

  license: GPL-2.0-or-later
  summary: Support functions,  data sets, and vignettes for the 'psych' package. Contains several
    of the biggest data sets for the 'psych' package as well as one vignette. A few
    helper functions for file manipulation are included as well. For more information,
    see the <https://personality-project.org/r/> web page.

  license_family: GPL2
  license_file:
    - '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - izahn
